Package: penCalc
Title: A package to calcaulate the monthly pension recieved by a
person after investing a portion of his wealth into an annuity. 
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Renuka", "Sane", email = "renukas@gmail.com, role = c("aut", "cre")),
person("Arjun", "Gupta", email = "arjung93@gmail.com, role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package to calcaulate the monthly pension recieved by a
person after investing a portion of his wealth into an annuity. This
package will estimate the income earned by the pensionee over his
lifetime by investing a portion of it into bonds, equity etc. This
package will estimate the the total income and monthly income  by an
individual. 
Depends: R (>= 3.2.5)
